snippet.title: Warframe’s Spring 2021 Content Lineup | Epic Games Store Spring Showcase
snippet.description:
Join Megan from Digital Extremes, developer of the free-to-play, sci-fi looter-shooter Warframe as she takes a closer look at the exciting content coming this spring to the Origin System!

Prepare for the coming storm in Call of the Tempestarii, featuring new, action-packed Railjack Missions and a Quest for the ghostly new Warframe, Sevagoth. Dance to your own rhythm with Octavia Prime Access, earn your wings during the upcoming Star Days, plus celebrate the Lunar New Year with special Customizations.

Whether you’re new to the Origin System or a seasoned Tenno, there’s never been a better time to play Warframe!  https://www.epicgames.com/store/en-US/product/warframe/home
